-----Explain how and why it is possible for a Hybrid Application to access native------
-------------------phone devices like location, calendar etc.--------------------------




Cordova is an intermediate, a layer if you would like to call it that way that allows you
to have access to hardware and providers of the phone throw it.

There is a number of Cordova plugins that grants you access to hardware
 The actual number of plug-ins as of this time counts to more than 70.

  See more here : http://ngcordova.com/docs/plugins/


